Scheduled Maintenances

New France Datacenter (2023 Infrastructure Part 1)

We will be setting up a new datacenter in France with a virtually unlimited amount of servers, based on the former zephyrheights server. Most services will become unavailable during that time, with the essential ones being transferred to a temporary server during the maintenance.
Scheduled from Jan 15 2023 to Jan 29 2023 (estimated)

New US Datacenter (2023 Infrastructure Part 2)

We will be setting up a new datacenter in the US with a virtually unlimited amount of servers, based on the former canterlot server. No public services should be affected by this maintenance.
Scheduled from Feb 01 2023 to Feb 15 2023 (estimated)

Bridlewood Cleanup (2023 Infrastructure Part 3)

We will be cleaning up the bridlewood server to optimise storage and performance. Some services could be affected by this maintenance, but we will try our best to avoid disruption.
Scheduled from Feb 17 2023 to Feb 19 2023 (estimated)
